## Suggested Technical Architecture

| Layer | Technology | Notes |
|-------|-----------|-------|
| **Frontend** | React Native or Flutter | Mobile-first; cross-platform |
| **Backend** | Node.js or Python (FastAPI) | API-driven architecture |
| **AI — Chat** | LLM (education + conversation) | Handles Q&A, explanations, onboarding |
| **AI — Recommendations** | Financial logic engine + ML models | Data-driven, rule-based with model augmentation |
| **Data Sources** | Market API, financials API, news API | See Section 9 |
| **Security** | OAuth 2.0, encryption at rest + in transit | Financial data requires strong security posture |

